. Scale bar = 500 km.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,151,418]" box="[198,916,151,178]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,348,151,177]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Bathymetry</emphasis>
: The only specimen was dredged at 
<quantity box="[776,836,152,178]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" unit="m" value="40.0">40 m</quantity>
